plugin.name: VST2413
plugin.author: Keijiro Takahashi
plugin.description: FM synthesizer based on YM2413 (OPLL) emulator. YM2413 is well known as low-cost FM sound chip, and was used on Sega Master System and FM-PAC sound expansion cartridge for MSX. VST2413 can resemble that warm texture of sound and may be well suited for use in 'post 8-bit era style' chiptune music.
